        <p>Collaborate and share tasks with others</p>
    <p style="font-weight: bolder;">Our goal is to simplify your life and help you achieve your goals more efficiently. Say goodbye to scattered sticky notes or forgotten tasks. With our Todo App, you can have all your tasks in one place, easily accessible from any device.</p>
